Approach looks good to me in general! Have some small questions. Super excited to get this merged. 

@rkooo567 could you also PTAL if this is something you expect for it to work?

Also, after we are aligned with the approach, let's add humanify fn to all the fields, we could have a few default functions that humanify common units (e.g., ms to human readable time, bytes to human readable size etc)

@jameerpathan111 Yeah! Agree that the universal ignoring the environment makes more sense instead of removing it completely! Though its depreciated its not completely removed yet :)

We also might need to raise a bug and get the reading of environment param fixed but let's get this in to unblock other tests !

ACK with a curious important question!
